properties.putsql-sql-statement:
INSERT INTO game_peeks (
    twitch_game_id,
    viewers,
    streams,
    channel_average_viewers, 
    channel_most_viewers, 
    rank,
    pulled_at
)
SELECT
    twitch_game_id,
    sum(viewers) as viewers,
    count(*) as streams,
    avg(viewers) as channel_average_viewers, 
    max(viewers) as channel_most_viewers, 
    rank() over (partition by pulled_at order by sum(viewers) desc) as rank,
    pulled_at
FROM stream_peeks
WHERE twitch_game_id IS NOT NULL
  AND pulled_at = '${pulled_at_attr}'
GROUP BY pulled_at, twitch_game_id
ON CONFLICT (pulled_at, twitch_game_id)
DO UPDATE SET
    viewers = EXCLUDED.viewers,
    streams = EXCLUDED.streams,
    channel_average_viewers = EXCLUDED.channel_average_viewers, 
    channel_most_viewers = EXCLUDED.channel_most_viewers, 
    rank = EXCLUDED.rank;
